    Konev for the pointer.
  * Add 001_no_xkb_in_pc_file.diff because we don't need x11proto-input-dev.
    Thanks Eugene Konev.

  [ Eugene Konev ]
  * Move locale data in separate libx11-data package. Make libx11-6 depend
    on it.
